summary:
Civil Industrial Engineer, with more than 12 years of relevant work experience in the electricity market business. Covering functions in the electricity distribution market through the study, development and implementation of tenders and the development and evaluation of projects, such as efficient public lighting, non-conventional renewable energies, energy efficiency, among others. Also strong knowledge in the development of the sale and / or trading of fuels, defining, evaluating and implementing new business development opportunities according to the strategy, resources and skills of the company and the needs of the market and target customers.

Extensive knowledge in construction and provision of services in the winter tourism sector, developing and operating real estate projects focused on mountain tourism
